  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/then-jesus-beholding-him-loved-him,Por el élder S. Mark Palmer,32,"Véase1 Nefi 8:37."
  2017,"04",/general-conference/2017/04/then-jesus-beholding-him-loved-him,Por el élder S. Mark Palmer,33,"1 Juan 4:18."
